  <name>ParaPara</name>
  <summary>An image viewer without library</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      An image viewer in which images are displayed as one of three styles:
      single, spread (book), continuous (scrolling),
      and that supports jpg, png, bmp, ico, gif files.
      animated gifs are also supported.
    </p>
  </description>
